"title": "5507: rope and cord",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5507",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Items normally used in domestic and military situations, but also used in Scripture in a symbolic sense to refer to bondage or constraint.</p>\n<h2>Various uses for rope and cord</h2>\n<h3>In clothes and furnishing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:28\">EXO 28:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:37\">EXO 28:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:38\">NUM 15:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:31\">1KI 20:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:6\">EST 1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:24\">EZK 27:24</a></p>\n<h3>For tents</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:18\">EXO 35:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:40\">EXO 39:40</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:37\">NUM 3:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:32\">NUM 4:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:2\">ISA 54:2</a></p>\n<h3>In sailing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:17\">ACT 27:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:32\">ACT 27:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:40\">ACT 27:40</a></p>\n<h3>In military use</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:13\">2SA 17:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:12\">PSA 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:2\">PSA 11:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:3\">JER 51:3</a></p>\n<h3>For rescue and escape</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:15\">JOS 2:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:12\">1SA 19:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6\">JER 38:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:13\">JER 38:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:25\">ACT 9:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:33\">2CO 11:33</a></p>\n<h3>To restrain animals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:5\">JOB 39:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:1-Job41:2\">JOB 41:1–41:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:9\">PSA 32:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:2\">MAT 21:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:2\">MRK 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:30\">LUK 19:30</a></p>\n<h3>To restrain people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:13-Judg15:14\">JDG 15:13–15:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:25\">EZK 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:8\">EZK 4:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:3\">MAT 14:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:17\">MRK 6:17</a></p>\n<h2>Rope and cord as symbols of bondage</h2>\n<h3>Of evil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:22\">PRO 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps129:4\">PSA 129:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:5\">PSA 140:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:18\">ISA 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:6\">ISA 58:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:6\">ROM 7:6</a></p>\n<h3>Of suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:16\">LUK 13:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:8\">JOB 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:8\">JOB 36:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:61\">PSA 119:61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:21\">DAN 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:3\">MAT 14:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:17\">MRK 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:1\">MRK 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:12\">JHN 18:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:24\">JHN 18:24</a></p>\n<h3>Of death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:4-Ps18:5\">PSA 18:4–18:5</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:6\">2SA 22:6</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:3\">PSA 116:3</a></p>\n<h2>Rope and cord as symbols of spiritual and emotional ties</h2>\n<h3>Symbols of loving relationships</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:4\">HOS 11:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:12\">ECC 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:20\">JER 10:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:2\">ROM 7:2</a></p>\n<h3>Symbols of obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:2-Prov7:3\">PRO 7:2–7:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:8\">DEU 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:18\">DEU 11:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:3\">PRO 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:20-Prov6:21\">PRO 6:20–6:21</a></p>\n<h3>Symbols of life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:6\">ECC 12:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:6\">PSA 16:6</a></p>",
